WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:05.088
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:09.092 --> 00:11.394
Don't work too hard there, Diane.

00:11.394 --> 00:12.896
I don't mind.

00:14.147 --> 00:15.982
Our wedding day draws ever nearer,

00:16.483 --> 00:18.985
and all this conditioning
is simply preparation

00:18.985 --> 00:21.488
for that special moment.

00:21.488 --> 00:23.356
When you and I exchange rings,

00:23.356 --> 00:26.276
my hands must be pristine,

00:26.276 --> 00:29.162
because everyone's eyes
will be on my fingers.

00:29.162 --> 00:32.582
And everyone's fingers'll
be down their throats.

00:34.084 --> 00:35.952
Oh, Carla.

00:35.952 --> 00:38.288
Sweet, pathetic Carla.

00:38.288 --> 00:41.791
Can't you see that I am
in far too good a mood

00:41.791 --> 00:45.045
to let your petty asides bother me?

00:45.045 --> 00:46.880
I'm afraid you'll just have to find

00:46.880 --> 00:49.766
some other way of... bugging me.

00:49.766 --> 00:51.885
If you insist.

00:51.885 --> 00:54.687
(screaming)

00:58.691 --> 01:03.063
(piano plays)

01:03.063 --> 01:05.364
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:05.364 --> 01:08.368
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:08.368 --> 01:11.371
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:11.371 --> 01:14.374
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:14.374 --> 01:20.413
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:20.413 --> 01:22.415
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:22.415 --> 01:27.921
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:27.921 --> 01:32.425
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:32.425 --> 01:34.928
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:34.928 --> 01:37.430
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:37.430 --> 01:42.936
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:42.936 --> 01:45.438
? You want to go where people know ?

01:45.438 --> 01:47.941
? People are all the same ?

01:47.941 --> 01:52.946
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

